-- pd.package: Bling components
name: fifthtry.github.io/bling

`fifthtry.github.io/bling` is a component library which contains various `ftd` 
components can be used on your pages. 

Bling is for making most content pages more interesting. Normally content pages, like a blog 
post, or news article etc, only have headings, single quote, image and code block. With bling 
we are trying to create rich variety of components to spice up such blog posts.

To use bling components on your web package, add below into `FPM.ftd` file:

-- cb.code:
lang: ftd

\-- fpm.dependency: fifthtry.github.io/bling
\-- fpm.auto-import: fifthtry.github.io/bling


